         /sigh</P><P>Part of the fundamental (fatal?) flaw with dots as they are now is the durations are too long.  If all our dots were the same damage and manacost as now but with a duration of 3 ticks for the fastest to say 6 ticks for the very longest many of our current problems would be far far less of a problem.</P><P>The *DAMAGE* per tick must increase to help us, increasing the duration merely adds to the existing flaw - not exactly something to jump for joy over.</P><P>The exception being our darkness line, since that is mostly used for snaring purposes and not damage an increase in duration there could be rather nice.  Shortening it would be unpleasant.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
